    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The primary acceptance criterion applied during review was RH < 1.05 (permissive threshold); the stricter RH < 1.0 threshold documented in the companion requirement was noted but not applied as the binding criterion for this decision cycle.",
